column5: Funny, I was just thinking today that I hadn't seen you around that much lately. Nice fish!
Nice to hear from you Simon. We have NO ice on whitefish or lake trout grounds here yet . Simcoe anyways. Soon I hope buddy. Great video. Super nice laker .
It’s finally frozen over near me around the 7th line of innisfil, maybe I’ll have to take a trip with the spud bar in a few days
Nice fish. Thanks for sharing the video.
Sweet Video.. I gotta get out!!
Simon, great to see you’re still letting us join you up north with your adventures
Thanks for sharing - enjoyed that video and glad to see you back online Simon Cheers Andrew
